<paragraph blockId="56.[189,1398,717,849]" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">
Length of male 
<quantity box="[380,472,717,744]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.9" pageId="56" pageNumber="57" unit="mm" value="8.9">8.9 mm</quantity>
(female unknown). Color mostly dark brown with some paler mottling. Style apophysis slightly but distinctly broadened preapically. Aedeagus with lateral ridges of atrium much more strongly sclerotized than medial part; shaft with pair of small digitiform processes mesad of longer lateral spines at apex.
</paragraph>
